Updated SURPRISE Retirement Lunch for Rich Jolly Luthers BBQ will be served Please RSVP Cc When Friday March AM PM GMT Central Time US Canada Where ECN C Rich Jolly will be retiring from ETS on May after years of service We wish Rich and his family the best of luck Richs last working day will be Friday March th so please join us in ECN C for a Surprise luncheon in his honor If there is anyone not on this list who has worked with Rich in the past or anyone you think would like to join us please forward this invitation and have them rsvp to Leigh Ann at Relaxation well deserved Embedded Microsoft Clip Gallery
